values: So, I actually forgot I had this account until today. Weird. Update: -Life is damn good -I graduate in December :) -I'll go to grad school shortly after (whichever school accepts me) -I take my GRE in August..kill me! -I'm (kinda) seeing someone. Good times -I might go to the beach this week with Curty Birdy and Jenny Due Di Tre -Curtis got into UC at Boulder! (congrats!) -Brutus is still a big ball of slut -I'm going running today with Alex (Yes! Off my lazy ass!) -I kind of want to get out of Miami for grad school..I wish I could afford it -I straightened my hair..although it'll be curly as soon as I wash it later today -I want one of these (Silky Anteater) That about covers it..How are you?

New shit: 
Relatively new job at another flight sim...the hours are stupid
New boyfriend: fun redneck giant :)
School's almost over...just to start back up in a few weeks
I'm uber broke
I'm happy.
Everyone needs to go to Texas de Brazil ASAP! It's so awesome ::creams:: They have a salad bar unlike any other, and the meat..all of it..is just AMAZING. All you can eat? Ole!

I am so bored I could kill myself. This job is mighty boring. I'm on day 3 of working at AeroServices..front desk. GOD DAMN IT! Why did I agree to do a 12 hour shift on the 4th of July. Feck! 

Hm..so yeah..the update. I am SINGLE for the first time in almost 3 years. It is mighty strange. Things didn't work out for a myriad of reasons. Summary: we were doomed. 

Yay! Pilots came and entertained me for a little bit. Apparently he has a Russian blue named Daisy. Good to know. Ok, now I'm back in kill me mode. 7.5 hours until I am out of here and I am STARVING. I apologize for venting. You probably stopped reading a while ago.
They might be in here ...That's what happens when i brush my hair when it's dry

I'm glad this week is over. Wednesday was hell. I had two tests and my brain was still on spring break so studying didn't go so well. Speaking of which...spring break was pretty gangsta. A week in Miami is what I needed. Friends, beach, eating..fun times

I have no clue if my account got deleted or just thrown into a pile of forgotten entries. Meh. I'm just at Kace's house waiting to go to BIG LOTS. So yeah, I live in Gainesville now. How weird is that? No parents, no rules, no MONEY..well, a little money. I need trabajo. I''m living off of my financial aid money now. Feck, I'm only taking 2 classes. I feel useless at Santa Fe Community College. Community college? What kind of shit is that? I feel like I've taken a step back. IF I get B's in my Precalculus Algebra and Trig classes I'll be off to UF! IF not, Miami here I come. Digression, anyone? So yeah. Gainesville is whatever. I have a whopping 2 friends: Chris (obviously) and Kace. I miss having a million friends. I miss having guy friends. They're the best. In due time.  Maybe I'll go to Miami on spring break. Maybe I'll go on a road trip to somewhere else. The plan was to go to France with the folks, but I don't know if that will happen. You never know. I feel like I'm back in high school writing in this livejournal. I wonder if anyone will even read it. Toodles for now, kiddies. Call me/ text me if you guys get bored enough of want to know which black abyss I fell into. (786) 487-5163

For those of you who haven't heard.. I got accepted to UF!! YAY! I should be out of miami by late December/early January!

"Congratulations!! Your application to the University of Florida for the 2007 Spring term has been approved. 

Official notification will arrive by mail, including important orientation and immunization information.

We look forward to seeing you on campus soon!"

Chris surprised me last night. He called and told me that he's in Miami. :) ::white girl dance:: I'll see him today at 4 when I get out of wizzork..yeah, that's a word. I swear! Oh holy crap. I just realized that in a little over a month it will be our 2 year anniversary. Man, I feel wierd saying that. 2YEARS! Holy shitballs it's insane.  It's a chisel. Killing my plant-like nature. Oh crapola. I'm hungry. Someone get me water and some sunshine.

Hey whoever actually reads this. 
     Long time no entry. Life has been pretty okay. Started school on monday (hiatus on tuesday and wednesday). I'm not taking any classes I like...and to top it off I have to go to north miami 5x a week to go to some of these classes. I just need to reach my goal of 60 credits by the end of the fall. Classes- Stellar astronomy, lab, modern euro history, spanish, pre calculus. Poop! I better get in to UF. I'm saving money now. Mom's not paying shit (she said it herself). I think it would be cool to not tell anyone about my plan of leaving, and just call everyone up a week before I leave (or even when I get to my destination) and be like "surprise! bye!" I don't know why I'd find that to be cool. I just do. Not even for other people. Just for me. I need to take an art class or something, at least paint in my spare time. I miss it. I was so looking forward to taking drawing..guess that's not happening. Poo for FIU. My boyfriend fell into the abyss of Gainesville, so I won't see him for another few months. Who does he think he is moving to get a better edumacation? Anyone wanna go fetch him for me? Yeah.. ready, set GO! 
     So I'm just sitting here at work doing nothing as always. Feel like clawing my eyes out. That's how unbusy it is here. Pilots, come hither! Ah! I don't want to go to school tomorrow. I hope I don't fail pre-cal. I better not. My GPA hates me enough as it is. 3.675. It used to be a 4.0, then down to 3.783, and now this. Yarr! I want a GPA that people can compete with. This is pansy shit right here. Kill me. I'm bantering. 

PS. If anyone's ever read The Perks of Being a Wallflower and wondered what song he was talking about..the beautiful one..go to my myspace. It's wonderful. Makes me sleepy. 
www.myspace.com/ibleedicewater
drama at the logvinov house. holy shit this is surprising. it's pretty damn bad.
damn it, fucker! he was supposed to be here at 2. a tad late, huh? thanks

I'm so pissed! I hate South Dakota! Fucking religious bastards. They're banning abortion. I don't know why this is such an issue. If one doesn't want to have a baby, she shouldn't have to. It's quite the burden, especially for a rape victim or a teen. Regardless of the circumstance, it should be fine to have an abortion. Never again will i watch the 700 club.
I have a job interview on monday!! hooray! Blockbuster on 122 and coral way. Let's see how this goes. I hope I  won't be broke forever.

i have the funniest sunburn. it's like someone roughly traced my bathinsuit with a pink sharpie. :) i went to the beach with ana and her friends lauren and ashley. it was fun. annie pierced her other nananana. pretty easily influenced. the piercer looked like a blonde, irish version of adam. at least i thought so. i wanted to give him a hug. he had this childish vibe to him. yesterday my parents had a party-like thing for our recently deceased friend tania. her daughters and friends came. it was pretty cool. their babies were so cute. mine! after, chris picked me up and we went to the movies. the inside mans was okay. it didn't have the shock value the director wanted. sheesh. oh yeah..i might might might go to uf next for my jr and sr year. we'll see how things go. baby # 1 baby # 2 what was i looking at? the folks

the worst of my worries is over. me so happy. bye bye human bio lab. let's see what grade i get. hm..only 5 more classes to go. tragic. i want the summer to come. anyone wanna take psychology of sexual behavior or philosophy with me? you know you wanna. all the cool kids are doing it. i need to find out if mdc has russian and how much it would cost. maybe i could do it in the summer. hm.. we'll see. i don't even know how it works. poop. so, yeah. might sleep over at ana's house, depending on if the beach thing works. we'll see what happens. i don't feel like staying up all night and then waking up early just to go home. fuck dat, nigga. Damn, i have class in 45 mins. what in the hell can i do to kill time until then?

I seriously should be studying. I have a french test tomorrow and a human bio lab final on tuesday. Man, this is pretty damn gay. Shoot me. I don't want to be here. I can't even concentrate. Waahaa! Yarr. Random noises. Sheet. I'm pretty thirsty,too. I wish I were elsewhere. Make this semester over!!! 

Oh yeah! Yesterday a Shaman came to my rel3308 class and did a ritual.It was alright. First we all split up into groups (earth, wind, fire, water) and each found our sounds and dances...our own rituals. Then we performed them together, got herbal liquid spit onto us (apparently healing us), and held hands and walkled around util we formed a really tight spiral..etc. There was more. It was so funny. At the end we had to yell out hardest. I did the girliest scream.. Chris sounded like a crazy drunk guy. Some girl sounded like a madman. It was hilarious. So, that was it. 

But seriously, MAKE THIS SEMESTER END!

Fuck cock shit ass mother fucker! Merde! My human bio test is on tuesday and my face should be in a book today. Wasted time until about 5. Big mistake. By the time I went to study my parents got home. Too loud. My  mom was watching TV and my dad was playing cello (if Jordan reads this he'd cream himself). I'm addicted to this song. It's awesome on my terms. It's hard to find good Russian music. Fa sho, nigga. I can't believe Karo is dead. It's wierd. I just saw her maybe a month ago and she seemed relatively fine. And POOF! Flat liner. That sucks. RIP kiddo. Lesson to everyone: Don't do drugs. Seriously. Sounds like a mom lecture, but it's quite helpful. It's highly unlikely that you ACTUALLY KNOW what you're taking. The high of rat poison. Tempting, huh? Are we all really THAT curious to know how it feels to lose a few brain cells? I like mine the way they are, thank you. So, my memory sucks, but it could be worse. This is probably the longest entry I have written in a while. Might as well amuse myself with some banter. Poop. I just can't get myself to pick up my human bio book. I'm practically done with all of my French shit. Damn it! French test tomorrow, human bio test tuesday, write a paper on wednesday. What the fuck is next? This is MIGHTY GAY!

Funny stuff...mind you, when I say funny I rarely mean funny. I was talking to my mom today and she was telling me random stories from when I was a munchkin. She said that when I was about 2 1/2 we were walking back home from the market and I was holding a green onion (I usually held stuff for her: loaf of bread, etc.). Usually when I did this people would tell me how cute I was helping my mommy hold the groceries. It was common so I got used to it. One time there was this old woman who could barely walk walking by me while I was holding the green onion and she didn't say anything. I jumped in front of her and stopped. Unfortunately she didn't notice me and toppled over me. My mom was so embarassed. After my mom helped her up, she said what I expected her to. Awe how cute I was. 
    Story #2: One day when I was maybe a year or more old and could barely walk- I used to lean on walls and after a few steps ((plop))- my  mom left some pins and needles on the sewing machine thinking that I couldn't get that far. She was in the kitchen and I waddled over do her with a bunch of pins and needles in my tiny hand. My mom freaked out and just took them from me and happily said thank you so I wouldn't do it again (reverse psychology).
    P.S. I just found out that I could work a record player at age 3. I had stories on records that I would play while going to sleep. Once if finished I would get up and turn it over. 
    Oh yeah! And when I got mad at my mom and cry I would blow my nose on her dress.
